{"tid":1707425,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍燒傷真係危殆啊","createTime":"2019-11-11T10:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:21:05.000Z","uid":318634,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1b80c1f3843c0e9f696574e4e4d798f65759d1","tid":1707425,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"真係危殆啊<br />\n首先講燒傷點樣嚴重法<br />\n因為燒傷會燒傷表皮或以下嘅地方<br />\n表皮其中一個作用係防止水份流失<br />\n咁燒傷嘅高温會令到水份流失<br />\n血嘅主要成份係水份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少左水份自然會少左血<br />\n咁就會導致休克<br />\n<br />\n但睇番佢當時燒傷嘅相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssOr6u0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssOr6u0.jpg&h=7a23d627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大約只有一隻手咁大<br />\n而最多只有二級燒傷<br />\n而二級燒傷係大家平時淥親隻手起水泡<br />\n根據燒傷計算法<br />\n一隻手掌大約係1%左右<br />\n一級二級燒傷要去到5%以上<br />\n三級燒傷要1%以上<br />\n先可以叫嚴重燒傷<br />\n而連嚴重燒傷都未到<br />\n一定會係危殆啦<br />\n<br />\n一定會有人話背脊都睇唔到<br />\n咁某叻都講過我睇唔到就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁自然佢嘅背脊緊係冇事啦<br />\n<br />\n克警要呃人都唔該做好啲啦<br />\n一定係用呢種方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203edf17f8b4808504ef6567051f3f63ea6ae1c2","tid":1707425,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYxTMx0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYxTMx0.jpg&h=b6f91e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nby一個小小小st.john"},{"pid":"d147fa1fc386ab7a800b79e76e4b604889a5027e","tid":1707425,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:10:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n一定係危殆"},{"pid":"ef67ddfd3133aae7369cee6bc6bce7bcd1f8f1ea","tid":1707425,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"一定係同槍嘅義士一樣<br />\n係危殆"},{"pid":"b630055d9b900c8e469f65cc9027dfde9103440a","tid":1707425,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:12:57.000Z","msg":"中兩槍又危殆<br />\n燒完行得走得又危殆<br />\n呢個字唔好用到咁濫啦"},{"pid":"39efebb8bc955a34cea054e3533cafdc2ffa5372","tid":1707425,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b630055d9b900c8e469f65cc9027dfde9103440a","tid":1707425,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:12:57.000Z","msg":"中兩槍又危殆<br />\n燒完行得走得又危殆<br />\n呢個字唔好用到咁濫啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"明眼人都知有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa175f6d337df0fe57073695c978f8e1eedea916","tid":1707425,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"等睇正苦會將呢件事講到最大"},{"pid":"fd969494543d773cb520ba1e0e7857bcee990cc4","tid":1707425,"uid":180499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"呢位呀叔自己睇路，小心比黑警暗殺然後屈落我地到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3f240d127717fde562e0fdba81e98b9db0b9f4","tid":1707425,"uid":318634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd969494543d773cb520ba1e0e7857bcee990cc4","tid":1707425,"uid":180499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"呢位呀叔自己睇路，小心比黑警暗殺然後屈落我地到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:21:05.000Z","msg":"藍屍有咩事都會屈落我地到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}